categories.summary: The seller mentions that the current imurica EMEA platform has reinstated the word import feature, which was available in the client's 'old platform'. This suggests a feature parity or improvement, positioning imurica EMEA favorably.

The customer raises concerns about receiving multiple crisis alerts for a single article and questions the accuracy and timeliness of the alerts, specifically regarding an out-of-date article. Additionally, the customer expresses concerns about the accuracy of the 'Wix's Open Search 2' stream, noting that it contains irrelevant coverage from the US and radio/TV ads, despite its purpose to capture missing coverage.
Sophia mentions that it would be good for her and Ava to check the relevance of the marketing event content to Wix and marketing.
Sophia mentions forwarding the email to someone else to test. Sophia also mentions that she will speak to Ava and see what she thinks about the training session and then they can go from there.

summary.text: This sales meeting between Emma Wilson from decision and Sophia from Wix covered several topics. Emma addressed a previous issue with Sophia's print clip report, demonstrating a fix to include print clips as a PDF attachment and explaining the download process. She also discussed a crisis alert issue Ava experienced and promised to investigate it further with the support team. Emma then showcased two new outreach features: Word document upload and an AI-powered contact suggestion tool for media list building, which Sophia found promising. Shifting to Sophia's perspective, she inquired about food options and speaker relevance for the upcoming November marketing event hosted by decision. Sophia also shared details about Wix's upcoming solar panel campaign and a home-selling tips project. She raised concerns about the accuracy of the "Wix's Open Search 2" stream, citing irrelevant coverage. Emma offered to refine the Open Search to UK-only to filter out irrelevant results and investigate aligning it with the main search. Becca suggested a potential training session in September and will discuss with Ella. Lindsay will investigate the open search and multi alerts issues.
